<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KUMA Test Case Builder - ผู้ช่วยสร้างกรณีทดสอบ AI (ฅ^•ﻌ•^ฅ)</title>
